{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2018/01/11/使用anko布局安卓应用.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4bda045d-689e-5938-be77-de031d27594e","excerpt":"使用 anko 布局安卓应用 build.gradle 配置 如wiki修改两处 使用 ConstraintLayout 修改build https://github.com/AckeeCZ/anko-constraint-layout 如何使用 缺点 anko 里面除了简单的布局有 DSL…","html":"<h1>使用 anko 布局安卓应用</h1>\n<h2>build.gradle 配置</h2>\n<p>如<a href=\"https://github.com/Kotlin/anko\">wiki</a>修改两处</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"gradle\"><pre class=\"language-gradle\"><code class=\"language-gradle\">// app(Module)\ndependencies {\n    implementation &quot;org.jetbrains.anko:anko:$anko_version&quot;\n    implementation &quot;org.jetbrains.anko:anko:$anko_version&quot;\n    implementation &quot;org.jetbrains.anko:anko-commons:$anko_version&quot;\n    implementation &quot;org.jetbrains.anko:anko-appcompat-v7:$anko_version&quot;\n    implementation &quot;org.jetbrains.anko:anko-recyclerview-v7:${anko_version}&quot;\n\n}</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"gradle\"><pre class=\"language-gradle\"><code class=\"language-gradle\">// app(Project)\nbuildscript {\n    ext.kotlin_version = &#39;1.2.10&#39;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>使用 ConstraintLayout</h2>\n<p>修改build</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/AckeeCZ/anko-constraint-layout\">https://github.com/AckeeCZ/anko-constraint-layout</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"gradle\"><pre class=\"language-gradle\"><code class=\"language-gradle\">dependencies {\n    implementation &#39;com.android.support.constraint:constraint-layout:1.1.0-beta4&#39;\n    implementation &#39;cz.ackee:anko-constraint-layout:0.6.5&#39;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>如何使用</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><pre class=\"language-kotlin\"><code class=\"language-kotlin\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> MainActivity<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">AppCompatActivity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">override</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fun</span> <span class=\"token function\">onCreate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>savedInstanceState bundle<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">onCreate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bundle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n        verticalLayout <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">editText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sayHello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                onClick <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toast</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, <span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token delimiter variable\">${</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>text<span class=\"token delimiter variable\">}</span></span>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>缺点</h2>\n<p>anko 里面除了简单的布局有 DSL 其它的需要去找(毕竟不是官方的)用起来还真不是特别方便</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2018/01/11/使用anko布局安卓应用.html","date":"January 11, 2018","title":"使用anko布局安卓应用"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2018/01/11/使用anko布局安卓应用.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2018/01/04/win10家庭版打开组策略.html","title":"win10家庭版打开组策略"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2018/01/24/完成了30个kotlin安卓挑战.html","title":"完成了30个kotlin安卓挑战"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}